The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, board-games
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | satire |
| Hobby   | card-games   | board-games |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | snake  |

