.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-3-6::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, photography
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage      | fanta       | tea   |
| Hobby         | photography | chess |
| Sport   | water-polo        | cricket  |

